### 1. Get first page of all matches (no filter)
GET http://localhost:8080/tennis_scoreboard_war_exploded/matches?page=1
Accept: text/html

###

### 2. Invalid page number (not a number)
# Expected: HTTP 400, "Page parameter must be a valid number."
GET http://localhost:8080/tennis_scoreboard_war_exploded/matches?page=abc
Accept: text/html

###

### 3. Negative page number
# Expected: HTTP 400, "Page number must be at least 1."
GET http://localhost:8080/tennis_scoreboard_war_exploded/matches?page=-5
Accept: text/html

###

### 4. Valid filter (player name = Roger)
# Expected: filtered matches with player "Roger"
GET http://localhost:8080/tennis_scoreboard_war_exploded/matches?filter_by_player_name=Roger
Accept: text/html

###

### 5. Filter with no results
# Expected: HTML response with "No matches found."
GET http://localhost:8080/tennis_scoreboard_war_exploded/matches?filter_by_player_name=xyz123
Accept: text/html

###

### 6. Filter + specific page
GET http://localhost:8080/tennis_scoreboard_war_exploded/matches?page=2&filter_by_player_name=Roger
Accept: text/html
